uote>部 5d iii 想放，有無興趣？仲未過一年保養 （應該）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有與趣 留個tg ok?"},{"pid":"1c9cafd63956486bd7ccae546c5d8b203fd6d1ab","tid":129548,"uid":79758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊6D，近來開始要接觸拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊5d mk4 或者 A7r2<br />\n巴打們點睇？比D意見小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5D4拍4k要1.5x<br />\n應該揀a7s2下話</blockquote><br />\n因為平時會影埋相，就覺得a7s2個像素唔夠大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49be14a2e1dc8d37a77e63bec901a600c57cfb72","tid":129548,"uid":79758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純計Body同畫質黎講，都無可能唔係A7S II<br />\n不過Sony有個大問題，就係佢自家啲鏡大部份都係fly-by-wire<br />\n<br />\n如果認真學拍片黎講，呢樣野超級麻煩<br />\n因為fly-by-wire只係方便無反auto-focus用<br />\nManual focus用fly-by-wire好難做得精準<br />\n<br />\n5D Mark IV：<br />\n好處係佢啲鏡大部份都係mechanical，manual時好用，auto-focus時聽聞都對得幾準跟得幾貼<br />\n<br />\n壞處就太多了，一無Peaking，二無log mode，三4K要Crop，四防震只可以靠支鏡（呢點比較小問題，頭三樣嚴重啲）<br />\n<br />\n利申：職業係拍片，我自己依家係A7S II加Canon鏡，全部Manual focus，拍片從來唔用Auto-focus，行內電影廣告亦無見過人用</blockquote><br />\n謝巴打詳盡分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSony嘅自家鏡真係。。太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但見普遍好多event / wedding嘅V都係sony機配canon鏡來拍片，抵好多"},{"pid":"f4b6a89ffbe1e388605adeaefc557ce5a6d7e7cd","tid":129548,"uid":26362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>部 5d iii 想放，有無興趣？仲未過一年保養 （應該）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有與趣 留個tg ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntg: thecats<br />\n<br />\n好少用tg，希望無比錯你"},{"pid":"f3691a4a7e57d3d2d0f8f7c19e46681